00:00:04.990 --> 00:00:08.100
And we're very pleased to have
Tamara Lackey with us today.

00:00:08.100 --> 00:00:10.160
She is going to be
discussing embracing

00:00:10.160 --> 00:00:13.610
self-consciousness, authentic
expression in portrait

00:00:13.610 --> 00:00:14.950
photography.

00:00:14.950 --> 00:00:18.660
Now she is a keynote speaker,
a fantastic photographer.

00:00:18.660 --> 00:00:21.730
She's been on the Martha Stewart
Show, Extreme Makeover, Home

00:00:21.730 --> 00:00:24.700
Edition, NBC's Today
Show, and she's also

00:00:24.700 --> 00:00:27.830
